SOLUTION 1 Solution with calcite and FeS2
        temp    20.
        units   mmol/l
        pH      7.0
        pe      -4.483
        Mg      5.78
        Cl     11.56    charge
        S       1.705e-3  
        Fe      1.279e-2 
